ygData.messageBody:
I think they were talking about the tarnished morning star... i've never heard of the
"enchanted MS" though I have been wrong before... the tarnished morning star is, or
was, dropped by some of the undead that just recently started roaming the Kithicore
Forest during the night. I heard a rumor, that they no longer dropped these however...
I hope that's not true because I really want one and they morning stars are no-drop
items... so if they no longer are being dropped in Kithicore i can never get one =(

-Eachann Bronzeleaf,
-cleric of Tunare, Tarew Marr
